00:00:01.580 --> 00:00:06.240
Professor Robert Shiller:
Next Wednesday we're having

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:10.146
David Swensen lecture to us.
He heads up the Yale

00:00:10.146 --> 00:00:14.985
endowment--or the investment of
the Yale endowment--and I have a

00:00:14.985 --> 00:00:18.750
